title: Owning a Piece of Hollywood History
itunes:title: Owning a Piece of Hollywood History
description:
Martin Nolan, Executive Director of Julien's Auctions, discusses the auction of Hollywood Legends memorabilia including an original Stormtrooper Helmet from Star Wars: A New Hope.
Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
